 I can give a kid a basketball, teach them to understand its value and how it can be used as a passport to success, am a fulfilled Coach.â€\r\n\r\nHobbies: Animation, Movie fanatic\r\n[/three_fourth_last]\r\n\r\n[divider_padding]\r\n\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n[image_frame style=\"framed_shadow\"]http://themes.mysitemyway.com/images/content/about_us.png[/image_frame]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[three_fourth_last]\r\n<h4>Simon Reed</h4>\r\n<h6>Chairman</h6>\r\nA parent and basketball fan, ever since heâ€™s son began his journey with the Club Simon along with wife Jackie have always been with the club and was always ready to lend a hand when ever needed. Since his sons journey with the club, Mr Reed together with his wife Jackie have been ever present in the clubs history. Mr Reed continues to be an inspiration to the club evoking dedication, passion and forward thinking in the clubs running. \r\n\r\nHobbies: Sports,\r\n[/three_fourth_last]\r\n\r\n[divider_padding]\r\n\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n[image_frame style=\"framed_shadow\"]http://themes.mysitemyway.com/images/content/about_us.png[/image_frame]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[three_fourth_last]\r\n<h4>Andy Gray</h4>\r\n<h6>Vice Chairman</h6>\r\nAndy has been part of Thunder since 2009, he is a huge basketball fan and has been a team manager for the junior england basketball team. Andy is the head of P.E at Dagenham Park School Church of England School.\r\n\r\nHobbies: Shopping, Dancing\r\n[/three_fourth_last]\r\n\r\n[divider_padding]\r\n\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n[image_frame style=\"framed_shadow\"]http://www.thunderbasketball.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/DSC_0933.jpg[/image_frame]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[three_fourth_last]\r\n<h4>Claire Clark</h4>\r\n<h6>Co-Founder</h6>\r\nClaire is co founder of Thunder and the head of Barking & Dagenham School Sports Partnership.\r\n\r\nHobbies: Traveling, Sports\r\n[/three_fourth_last]\r\n\r\n[divider_padding]\r\n\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n[image_frame style=\"framed_shadow\"]http://themes.mysitemywa