 and management team from around the globe. The latest arrival is French student Solene Youbi, 20 years old who has arrived as an intern to the clubs backroom staff. Youbi who has played basketball since the age of 6, is currently in business and management school with the club on a 3 month internship. <a href=\"http://www.thunderbasketball.co.uk/solene-youbi-internship/\" title=\"SOLENE YOUBI INTERNSHIP\"><em>Read more</em></a>\r\n\r\nWith a huge drive and passion for the sport, Youbi has been welcomed to the club with open arms and has already made an impact behind the scenes. Youbi stated \"This is a great experience for me and I am delighted that the club has taken me on board to assist in all business-related aspects off the court. This is an exciting time for the club having just been promoted and I look foward to helping the club move forward.\"\r\nRavidson Teixeira, Thunders Head of Basketball Operations proclaimed \"France is an excellent basketball nation with various different business and basketball related aspects. It is always beneficial for us to have someone on board who can show us some of the more successful solutions they have implemented there.\" \r\n','SOLENE YOUBI INTERNSHIP','','inherit','closed','closed','','1573-revision-v1','','','2015-04-27 08:03:14','2015-04-27 08:03:14','',1573,'http://www.thunderbasketball.co.uk/1573-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1583,1,'2015-04-27 08:20:04','2015-04-27 08:20:04','','hi_big_e_min_blue','','inherit','closed','closed','','hi_big_e_min_blue','','','2015-04-27 08:20:04','2015-04-27 08:20:04','',938,'http://www.thunderbasketball.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/hi_big_e_min_blue.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1586,1,'2015-04-27 08:24:25','2015-04-27 08:24:25','<p><h6>BAD Thunder Health Hoops</h6></p>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.thunderbasketball.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/hi_big_e_min_blue.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.thunderbasketball.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/hi_big_e_m